{"tid":897290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實開槍制伏唔應該表揚","createTime":"2018-11-10T18:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T16:00:18.000Z","uid":24559,"like":56,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f2dc76d56a02bdaaec0b9c4ba82b232e6c4b3833","tid":897290,"uid":24559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"首先希望大家理性討論<br />\n<br />\n開槍應該係<span style=\"color: red;\">最終手段</span><br />\n如果採用左最終手段後<span style=\"color: red;\">得到表揚</span><br />\n間接鼓吹開槍壓制<br />\n取而代之<br />\n以後出現激進protest-&gt;開槍鎮壓-&gt;64 v.2<br />\n<br />\n警員唔係唔可以開槍<br />\n但呢件事絕對唔可以表揚<br />\n成件事應該係社會悲劇<br />\n警方應該處於中立並自我檢討<br />\n尋求改善或者更好既做法<br />\n而唔係一尾表揚同保護自己友<br />\n我唔希望第時有議員掟野又話致命武器<br />\n又有過度武力<br />\n<br />\n開槍係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔應該表揚</span></span>架"},{"pid":"bf0df9e6d673f7e95ffb948cbbc3b38773c04b42","tid":897290,"uid":140769,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:39:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5987110f54b7543748d35671a6992b4df6090739","tid":897290,"uid":164913,"like":24,"dislike":20,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d020ee2c9b5580d97e8d437be0465d42f96d7e0","tid":897290,"uid":92459,"like":9,"dislike":15,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:46:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母成班左膠<br />\n唔開槍就可能有社會悲劇啦<br />\n有人攞刀衝向你，仲記得講警戒詞再開槍，<br />\n周圍咁多市民，如果唔開槍，有咩傷亡邊個負責?"},{"pid":"d61595dbe9bec34fc9f2a2c3b2c18b47be6e4f80","tid":897290,"uid":140769,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:49:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"605690e10e80c3e1919a6c7beed4a8fe1f8ebbe0","tid":897290,"uid":92459,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:50:01.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n你話開槍打示威者就有問題<br />\n快速制服犯人，避免傷亡<br />\n值得表揚"},{"pid":"17de682503eeb79faa673b978db366b32fd1ca69","tid":897290,"uid":24559,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:59:34.000Z","msg":"首先希望大家唔好將件事代入左女警開槍事件度<br />\n第二 無論任何時候警方都應該有humble既心態<br />\n係事件中尋求進步先至係最佳選擇<br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好忘記, 手槍都係極度危險既致命武器<br />\n應該要更嚴謹同謹慎使用<br />\n<br />\n所以我認為應該配帶遠距離又低殺傷力既武器<br />\n例如電槍"},{"pid":"313560647122e02d7b55e17698a115baa4fc2dfa","tid":897290,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T19:03:15.000Z","msg":"除咗好似旺角條傻鳩，好似好少純粹因爲開槍而獲表揚"},{"pid":"f5a81c00074f5db5c45d062ab2f3b07d371e5d08","tid":897290,"uid":205530,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T19:06:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"125e4177fb8260f7b13eaafd0cdd36c60bffbea9","tid":897290,"uid":205530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T19:10:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb88adc6627725002d106800305fd31192081611","tid":897290,"uid":69213,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T19:29:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9f58b8db74d573de9f06717c6c3d5a4eb881f46","tid":897290,"uid":140769,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T19:34:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"643fe76f8f9c6a1b2a50ae1297f454397409d1c6","tid":897290,"uid":69213,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T19:35:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62c89965d1d624c623020d3f421884f239237f2f","tid":897290,"uid":24559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"313560647122e02d7b55e17698a115baa4fc2dfa","tid":897290,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T19:03:15.000Z","msg":"除咗好似旺角條傻鳩，好似好少純粹因爲開槍而獲表揚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"拉上少少咪見到有個傻鳩表揚緊佢"},{"pid":"7b244249c5f05fc49afbb43509fad9140cff6d18","tid":897290,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d020ee2c9b5580d97e8d437be0465d42f96d7e0","tid":897290,"uid":92459,"like":9,"dislike":15,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:46:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母成班左膠<br />\n唔開槍就可能有社會悲劇啦<br />\n有人攞刀衝向你，仲記得講警戒詞再開槍，<br />\n周圍咁多市民，如果唔開槍，有咩傷亡邊個負責?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"做得啱還做得啱，但係大肆宣傳就唔啱"},{"pid":"0f8384c98f342fbe0bebeb3cffeffffadeca94f2","tid":897290,"uid":15548,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"你搞清楚先。<br />\n向示威遊行參與者開槍，打壓緊既係言論自由、集會自由，呢啲係現代文明社會上人民既基本權利。<br />\n一條友係地鐵站拎把cutter出黎舞，果啲係痴撚線。"},{"pid":"e088c72b3690a6c82f44eb906cb730d6ee992b90","tid":897290,"uid":213300,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:39:42.000Z","msg":"唔知有咩好討論<br />\n如果開槍係為民除害嘅<br />\n當然值得表揚<br />\n不必要開槍而開槍就抵鬧<br />\n樓主唔好將兩個不同情況擺埋一齊 混淆視聽"},{"pid":"d73ce9bca05eab3172c3f40fe1a61913a6e5969d","tid":897290,"uid":147047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"根本班黑京就恥地無銀"},{"pid":"ff2c3536db8602ad83aa138b2ae602f8c9e0b75b","tid":897290,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"啲人拎條𠝹刀佬同義士比係侮辱緊班義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f10ea77aa0e0c3adb5edfc7421a81e142c5d9c","tid":897290,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"講真 呢啲係差佬份內事"},{"pid":"e855319c47b79aca60ca0523b612309f8f98eea3","tid":897290,"uid":121546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:33:04.000Z","msg":"係係香港好少發生咁既事,大家覺得精彩姐<br />\n美國警察成日都要開槍保護自己,果邊都冇人care"},{"pid":"8a237c4a7ad0b0b0e598518d193561dc9ac63172","tid":897290,"uid":24559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff2c3536db8602ad83aa138b2ae602f8c9e0b75b","tid":897290,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"啲人拎條𠝹刀佬同義士比係侮辱緊班義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/